{"tid":83034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前女F4成員劉樂妍 :給中國人磕頭怒嗆世上沒有台灣國","createTime":"2017-01-16T12:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T16:47:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89fe2e3c028c9dcfcaa06b6cbf688ce7ec094c36","tid":83034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/01/16/php2uEbxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2Fphp2uEbxr.jpg&h=d86f744f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸遼寧艦日前進入台灣海峽，引發國軍高度關注，前女F4成員劉樂妍卻發文表示「喜歡看風景就讓它看啊」，認為「台灣人只要是中國人，他們永遠不會打我們，而且會保護我們。」並不斷積極表態自己是「中國人」，引發台灣部分網友抨擊，遭酸「抱中國大腿」，更要她別用台灣健保，對此劉樂妍激烈反擊，嗆聲：「我還要給中國人磕頭」、「世界上沒有台灣國這個國籍」！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/01/16/phpwPtPjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2FphpwPtPjD.jpg&h=bc290ccb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為遼寧艦事件，劉樂妍被民進黨立委黃偉哲酸是「脫星」，並認為她失言、低智商，更遭部分台灣網友抨擊「為人民幣下跪」、「別用台灣健保」等。對此，她憤怒反嗆：「我不但跪在中國人面前，我還要給中國人磕頭。因為我是中國人的後代！」 <br />\n<br />\n劉樂妍表示「因為忠，所以我從來沒有說過我是中華人民共和國人。因為孝，所以我也沒有忘記過我是祖籍湖北的台灣人。」強調自己賺的錢一直打回台灣，是對台灣是有貢獻的人，質問：「憑什麼要我不會能用台灣健保？要我退出台灣國籍？」更加碼嗆聲：「世界上沒有台灣國這個國籍」，反酸罵她的網友：「難道你們這些人全部都是洪素珠嗎？」"},{"pid":"6e163145ee36dd3db689e051bea5713c279104ef","tid":83034,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"台灣宇宙漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n膠都費事畀"},{"pid":"52a86e8d8ff8eae2cc29edde0b518f8d38db0991","tid":83034,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"我是祖籍湖北的台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔怪得"},{"pid":"f28eb32f497abf1e468092334d872325cf85d100","tid":83034,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"「憑什麼要我不會能用台灣健保？要我退出台灣國籍？」<br />\n「世界上沒有台灣國這個國籍」<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da969dc846e4121bbe7a22fa261a8ccfdf5a1622","tid":83034,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"雞味濃<br />\n不但要給支那跪還要含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5f43324665b09cce06a53c5cf751c375e38fd9","tid":83034,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「憑什麼要我不會能用台灣健保？要我退出台灣國籍？」<br />\n「世界上沒有台灣國這個國籍」<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dba78614678264480e94ba8b5a143af7bdf7b6","tid":83034,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af8622d956275430e4839d4a6fe2d40bc16eff6c","tid":83034,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e70116ac643308b5c87114da8d750afe289db494","tid":83034,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係女F4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nf cup x 4"},{"pid":"78cd69c7f5fe67e6f084a1ae40435270bfc5580d","tid":83034,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e03c567564a0d11fbdbf6814b41e4408cd01b2","tid":83034,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"係咪史前偶像"},{"pid":"1593318289dae673cd1a28c2e6a30074fa0